About Me

Hello, I'm Muhammad Saqib Rafique, a passionate and goal-driven Senior Software Engineer specializing in front-end development. With extensive experience in Angular, TypeScript, HTML, and CSS, I have led teams and delivered high-quality, responsive applications. I thrive on solving complex problems and ensuring seamless integration between front-end and back-end systems. I have a track record of mentoring junior developers and optimizing workflows, having built successful projects like the Zuub Dental RCM platform and a Slack-integrated reporting system for Kayak. I am committed to clean code and best practices to drive success and innovation.
